data.description: Welcome to this charming like-new home in the highly desirable Sterling Ridge. This two-story residence boasts five spacious bedrooms and three bathrooms, offering a seamless blend of comfort and contemporary living. A spacious bedroom and full bathroom downstairs, perfect for hosting guests or in-laws. Positioned on a tranquil cul-de-sac street, the property welcomes you with a charming front porch leading into a spacious living area with ceramic tile flooring. The inviting island kitchen is complete with modern amenities including stainless steel appliances. An extra room serves as a versatile study/office, catering to your lifestyle needs. This home features solar panels, keep your electric bill for the large home to less than $10/month. Zoned within sought-after Comal ISD, seize the opportunity to own a meticulously maintained home in this welcoming community of Sterling Ridge.
